# 87.1  reg_nv.js has FALLOUT_REGISTRY.magazines array
Check ([bool]($nvRegSrc87 -match 'magazines\s*:\s*\[')) "reg_nv.js has FALLOUT_REGISTRY.magazines array (FNV-only)"

# 87.2  exactly 14 entries
