# ===========================================================
# Suite 131 -- U1: getSystemDirective() decomposition + GA-5 retirement
# (Step 2 / v2.8.0 Phase 0). Structural guards that the directive is now
# composed from named per-section builders, plus a Protocol 14 golden-master
